msgid "The coupon can only be claimed on future orders."
msgstr "ຄູປອງນີ້ສາມາດແລກໄດ້ໃນໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຄັ້ງຕໍ່ໄປເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. module: sale_loyalty
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_loyalty/models/sale_order.py:0
