#. module: sale_loyalty
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_loyalty/models/sale_order.py:0
msgid ""
"This discount (%(discount)s) is not compatible with \"%(other_discount)s\". "
"Please remove it in order to apply this one."
msgstr ""
"ສ່ວນຫຼຸດນີ້ (%(discount)s) ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ຮ່ວມກັບ \"%(other_discount)s\" ໄດ້. ກະລຸນາລົບອອກກ່ອນເ"
"ພື່ອຈະນຳໃຊ້ອັນນີ້."

#. module: sale_loyalty
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/sale_loyalty/models/sale_order.py:0
